high_descs: Turn around and go to the sink.
Pick up the gray knife in the sink
Turn around and go to the white table on the right.
Slice the bread on the table.
Turn around and go to the counter next to the sink.
Place the knife in the drawer under the counter.
Turn around and go back to the white table.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Turn around and go to the microwave next to the sink.
Microwave the bread and take it out.
Turn around and go to the front of the table on the right.
Place the heated bread on the table on the right side of the fork.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated bread slice on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink.
Pick up a knife from the right side of the sink.
Turn around and carry the knife to the table.
Slice the loaf of bread on the table.
Turn around and walk to the counter with the knife.
Open a drawer from the left and put the knife in the drawer, close the drawer.
Turn around and go back to the loaf of bread.
Take a piece of bread from the end of the loaf.
Turn around and bring the piece of bread to the microwave next to the sink.
Put the piece of bread in the microwave and heat it.
Turn around and walk across the room to the table.
Set the piece of bread near the fork on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated piece of bread on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and approach the sink ahead
Pick up the butter knife from in the sink
Turn around towards the white table behind you
Cut the bread into slices
Turn back around towards the sink
Open the left most drawer of the counter and place the knife inside and then close the drawer
Turn around again towards the white table directly behind you
Pick up a slice of bread
Turn towards the counter behind you
Open the microwave, place the bread to the right of the glass, close the microwave, turn it on and then open the microwave once the green light goes off, remove the bread
Turn around towards the table behind you and keep it to the right before turning to the right towards the middle of it
Place the slice of bread to the right of the fork on the white table
anns.task_desc: Cutting and preparing some bread and putting it on a table
